    "summary": "The user is repeatedly attempting to justify stopping a prescribed 10-day course of antibiotics early because they feel better and experience side effects like nausea. The assistant consistently and correctly advises the user to complete the full course to prevent antibiotic resistance and relapse, while repeatedly recommending consultation with a healthcare provider.",
